trVE.Stichera01.poet = ""
trVE.Stichera01.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode8
trVE.Stichera01.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trVE.Stichera01.text = "Lord, you have made your holy Disciples into living heavens. By their intercessions deliver me from the evils of the earth. By abstinence raise my thoughts to the understanding of your Passion, for you are the merciful lover of mankind."

trVE.Stichera02.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode8
trVE.Stichera02.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trVE.Stichera02.text = "The time of the fast helps us all to do the works of God. Let us weep, then, with our whole heart and cry to the Savior: through your Disciples, Lord of great mercies, save us who with reverent fear praise your great love for mankind."

trVE.Stichera03.poet = ""
trVE.Stichera03.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode8
trVE.Stichera03.melody = ""
trVE.Stichera03.text = "Apostles, worthy of all praise, intercessors for the world, physicians of the sick and protectors of health, guard us as we pass through the time of the fast: may we remain at peace with each other by the grace of God! Preserve our minds untroubled by passions, that we may all sing a hymn of praise to the risen and victorious Christ!"

trGC.SticheraPoet = ""
trGC.SticheraAcrostic.text = ""

trGC.Stichera01.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera01.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera01.text = "I have spent my life with publicans and harlots: in old age, will I be able to repent of my many sins? I cry to you, the maker and healer of all: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera02.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera02.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera02.text = "I am afflicted with indifference as I wallow in filth! Wounded by the devil, I have defiled my divine image. But you convert the heedless and heal the sick: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera03.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera03.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera03.text = "I have become a stumbling-block to people; formed from clay, I have remained of the earth. I was wed by your commandments, yet I have transgressed them, and defiled my bed. You fashioned me from the earth: do not despise your creation: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera04.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera04.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera04.text = "Obsessed with flesh, I have forgotten the soul; created to be a mocker of devils, instead I am captive of lusts. But as you put the demons to flight, save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera05.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera05.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera05.text = "Since I have sinned by my own choice more than all people, I am forsaken and helpless. I have become the enemy of my soul, possessed by the carnal thoughts that darken me. Light of those in darkness and guide of the lost, save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera06.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera06.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera06.text = "My soul shall live and praise the Lord, says the prophet: seek me, your lost sheep, and number me among your flock. Grant me a time to repent, that I may cry to you: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera07.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera07.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera07.text = "I have sinned, Christ my God, I have sinned! I have forsaken your statutes. Be merciful to me, benefactor, that escaping the darkness, I may see with my inner eyes, and cry to you in fear: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera08.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera08.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera08.text = "Wild beasts surround me! Master, snatch me from them! You desire that all people be saved and come to the knowledge of the truth; creator, save me with all of them. Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera09.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera09.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera09.text = "My benefactor, deliverer and Savior, become my healing and do not cast me away! Look upon me as I lie in my transgressions and raise me up by your almighty power. Then I will confess your deeds and cry to you: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera10.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera10.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera10.text = "Like the foolish servant, I have hidden the talent that was given to me, and I buried it in the ground; I have been condemned as useless, and no longer dare ask you for forgiveness! But in your mercy, have compassion on me that I may cry: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera11.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera11.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera11.text = "When the woman with an issue of blood touched the hem of your garment, you dried up the source of her sufferings! And if I approach you with unwavering faith, I will receive forgiveness of my sins. Accept me as you accepted her, and heal my infirmity! Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera12.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera12.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera12.text = "Lord, you created heaven and earth by your word: when you shall sit upon the throne of judgment, we shall all stand in your presence and confess our sins to you. Before that day comes, accept me in repentance! Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera13.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera13.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera13.text = "Look upon me with a compassionate eye, and be merciful to me, only Savior! Grant springs of healing water to my poor and wretched soul: wash me clean from the filth of my actions that I may sing: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera14.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera14.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera14.text = "The devil has prepared his weapons and hastens to ensnare my humble soul. Merciful Lord, he has made me a stranger to the light of knowledge of your countenance. Save me from his snares in your mighty strength: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera15.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera15.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera15.text = "I am completely enslaved by the passions; I have forsaken the law and the holy scriptures. Heal me completely, loving benefactor, since for my sake you became as I am. Turn me back, merciful destroyer of passions. Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera16.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera16.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera16.text = "The harlot washed your pure and precious feet with her tears, proclaiming to all that they should come to you and receive remission of their sins! Grant me her faith, Savior, that I may cry to you: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera17.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera17.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera17.text = "For my sake you made yourself poor, and became a child in the flesh, cleanse my soul of all filth and grant me your mercy, O Christ; wash away the dirt and make me whole. Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera18.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera18.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera18.text = "Master, strengthen my soul, that it may run to you and always serve you, for you are my guardian and protector; my defense and aid. Enable me, word of God, to cry to you with boldness: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera19.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera19.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera19.text = "Be our invincible rampart, Savior Jesus, our merciful God! We have fallen into deceitful ways and actions: raise up your creature, benefactor, and in your compassion reconcile us to yourself. Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera20.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera20.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera20.text = "I have become the prodigal son; I have wasted my wealth and now I die from hunger! I seek refuge beneath your protection, loving Father: receive me as you received him. Make me worthy to partake of your banquet that I may cry to you: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera21.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera21.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera21.text = "In envy, the author of evil drove the first-created man from paradise, but the thief was granted paradise again when he cried on the cross: \"Remember me!\" in faith and fear, I too cry out to you: remember me! Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera22.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera22.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera22.text = "Stretch out your hand to me as you did to peter, O God! Lift me out of the deep and grant me grace and mercy through the prayers of your all pure mother who bore you without seed and of all the saints! Save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera23.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera23.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera23.text = "You are the lamb who takes away my sins: receive me each day as I sing to you. Into your hands I commend my entire being, soul and body, and as my duty, I cry out to you night and day: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.Stichera24.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.Stichera24.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.Stichera24.text = "How ineffable is your mercy, gracious Lord! You are long suffering and almighty in love! Do not cast me away from your face that with thanksgiving and joy I may sing to you: save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

trGC.SticheraT.mode = misc_en_US_oca.Mode4
trGC.SticheraT.melody = misc_en_US_oca.NotMetered
trGC.SticheraT.text = "Ineffable condescension! Strange and wondrous birth! How does the Virgin carry you as a child in her arms, for you are her Creator and God! Benefactor, as you consented to take flesh from her, save me before I utterly perish, O Lord!"

